# Login System Implementation Plan

This plan details the implementation of a modern login screen backed by a local SQL Server.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]  
> To proceed with the **Senior Sistemas** (Payroll/HR) integration, I need some technical clarification:
> 1. **Integration Method**: Does your Senior system expose a REST/SOAP API (e.g., Senior X or G5 APIs), or do you want to connect directly to its Database views (SQL Server/Oracle) via our C# backend? If via API/DB, please provide the endpoint/IP.
> 2. **Data Scope**: What exact information do you want to pull into the "DP" menu of our new Dashboard? (e.g., employee list, payslips/holerite, vacation balances, or just use Senior's data to sync logins?)

## Proposed Changes

### Database Setup
A SQL script to create a `Users` table storing `Username`, `PasswordHash`, and `Email`.

